post.desc:
Legit had a brainf#ck trying to figure out "**力で勝てる訳ないでしょ**". Like, at first for some reason I assumed Sanae was saying it, so I thought it's something like:
- There's no way I can win if it comes to strength.

But then I realized that it's most definitely Kogasa saying it, and in this case I think it's either:
- There's no way I can win if I use just strength.
- There's no way you can win if it comes to strength.
